經濟衰退一齊黎，對平民百姓而言佢地更加唔敢洗錢，會將Ｄ錢放係銀行，個社會唔消費就變做惡性循環，令到經濟衰落去。所以Ｄ人情願要通漲好過通縮，因為經濟增長先會帶來同漲。"},{"pid":"72d535a4b9c958dcfecde7824633dae0cea162b9","tid":1758603,"uid":165213,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:52:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府可以係我地到拎錢 而我地唔多會發覺</span></span>"},{"pid":"39a8aa38e6ec0d1dcb8f512c74ed6ffdb72e3526","tid":1758603,"uid":66242,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d4091c91f6d604fab3da66093ad9f8f5e2dd745f","tid":1758603,"uid":70301,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"64229e9e665f7b3ff265a8d74c430ef48275ccee","tid":1758603,"uid":193563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"點解每年通脹設目標2%<br />\n對唔識投資既人好不利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:20:21.000Z","msg":"貨幣緩慢貶值會令你覺得&ldquo;錢&rdquo;呢樣嘢越來越唔值錢，要快啲用咗佢，從而達到刺激經濟，刺激消費嘅效果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:57:46.000Z","msg":"啱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n刺激消費<br />\n加速消耗地球資源<br />\n三戰早日降臨<br />\n人類盡快喺地球消失<br />\n達到浴火重生嘅效果<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e656170d9a25ffe630713c1fe35057b13f3ab2a0","tid":1758603,"uid":57844,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"39a8aa38e6ec0d1dcb8f512c74ed6ffdb72e3526","tid":1758603,"uid":66242,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d4091c91f6d604fab3da66093ad9f8f5e2dd745f","tid":1758603,"uid":70301,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"64229e9e665f7b3ff265a8d74c430ef48275ccee","tid":1758603,"uid":193563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"點解每年通脹設目標2%<br />\n對唔識投資既人好不利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:20:21.000Z","msg":"貨幣緩慢貶值會令你覺得&ldquo;錢&rdquo;呢樣嘢越來越唔值錢，要快啲用咗佢，從而達到刺激經濟，刺激消費嘅效果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:57:46.000Z","msg":"啱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n刺激消費<br />\n加速消耗地球資源<br />\n